{"tid":1379063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[發惡夢]  係閪鐶比恐龍咬","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T19:36:21.000Z","uid":50252,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"550b1965a5effae78136f67f2ed9b28bde8a8fcd","tid":1379063,"uid":50252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"隻恐龍已經咬住我個袋<br />\n我轉身一個鞭拳 隻恐龍就放口<br />\n係呀! 我走到呀 但我好撚內疚呀仆街<br />\n因為已經見到身邊既人比恐龍食緊<br />\n我救唔到呀 點解要推人呀<br />\n<br />\n我冇興趣屌人 <br />\n但如果我係恐龍<br />\n見到你地 唔齊裝備<br />\n放幾次煙直接退退退<br />\n肚餓唔食你食邊個？<br />\n<br />\n返到去尚還 覺得成件事唔到左D<br />\n雖然最後兄弟行山累撚過閪<br />\n<br />\nsorry 我語氣重左 <br />\n但因為我依加嬲到醒左<br />\n訓唔返覺"},{"pid":"6f385b6467f1e05e4e592cea569794bbf3b02a16","tid":1379063,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"手足多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b189ad376cdf592d52b6cdf2948ee410859b6720","tid":1379063,"uid":50252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f385b6467f1e05e4e592cea569794bbf3b02a16","tid":1379063,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"手足多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我無野講"},{"pid":"c0f019a3638042b12985086af60c67c97692fdfd","tid":1379063,"uid":50252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"希望 Jurassic World 中/後既各位發夢兄弟<br />\n有方法分別到咩係 跑 / 快步 / 退(1212)"},{"pid":"0ae35ca0b1fa1f3880b4c2312d770429595bcbf2","tid":1379063,"uid":50252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f019a3638042b12985086af60c67c97692fdfd","tid":1379063,"uid":50252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1